# SELF-LIBRARY operator books — reference strings

## `predictive-history`

When the operator writes **`predictive-history`** (hyphenated) or clearly means **the SELF-LIBRARY Predictive History book**, interpret that as **LIB-0149**: the multivolume operator corpus under **`research/external/work-jiang/`**, indexed from **`users/grace-mar/SELF-LIBRARY/predictive-history`** (symlink). Use **`BOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md`**, **`STATUS.md`**, and the lecture/analysis tree there — not a different project.

**Do not** resolve **`predictive-history`** to **`research/external/youtube-channels/predictive-history/`** (that is **LIB-0151**, the YouTube transcript library). For that bundle, use explicit wording: **Predictive History YouTube transcript library**, **LIB-0151**, or the full path **`youtube-channels/predictive-history`**.

If scope is ambiguous, ask once or default to **LIB-0149** when the hyphenated form appears.

## `strategy-notebook`

When the operator writes **`strategy-notebook`** (hyphenated) or clearly means **the SELF-LIBRARY strategy notebook book**, interpret that as **LIB-0153**: **`docs/skill-work/work-strategy/strategy-notebook/`**, indexed from **`users/grace-mar/SELF-LIBRARY/strategy-notebook`** (symlink). Primary artifacts: **`README.md`**, **`STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md`**, **`STATUS.md`**, **`chapters/YYYY-MM/knots/`** (pages) + **`days.md`** (continuity) + **`meta.md`** (month scaffold).

**Do not** treat **`strategy-notebook`** as **`STRATEGY.md`** (work-strategy milestone / watches ledger — different file, optional promotion target from the notebook). Do not substitute the whole **`work-strategy/`** lane for the notebook unless the operator names that scope.

If scope is ambiguous, ask once or default to **LIB-0153** when the hyphenated form appears.
